title: China today and her Ancient Treasures (History Art).pdf
description:
pdf / english / 1985 Abrams / ISBN10 0810907984 / 430 pages / 72.6 MB


China Today and Her Ancient Treasures presents a spectacular panorama ranging from recently excavated 2,300-year-old life-size ceramic warriors, horses, and chariots to life and art in the People's Republic of China today. Magnificent pagodas, exotic gardens, the Great Wall, the fabled palaces of the Forbidden City, are all presented
in marvelous full-color photographs
